{
  "texts": [
    "The proposed SSEHCET has six layers: 1) The Sensing layer, which includes IoT sensors that are often situated on or inside patients' bodies and transfer data to smartphones.",
    "2) The edge layer, which comprises components that gather data near IoT devices.",
    "3) The communication layer makes use of the capabilities of 5G technology to send patient data across many levels effectively.",
    "4) Cloud servers or other powerful computers comprise the storage layer.",
    "5) A security layer that uses BCT to transmit and retain patient data securely."
  ]
}